      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through benchmark problems relevant to blood-pump flow regimes.",
      "rationale": "The solver was verified against the FDA benchmark nozzle and backward-facing step problems. Velocity profiles and pressure drop predictions agree with published DNS data within 3%, confirming correct discretization of the Navier-Stokes equations in the relevant Reynolds-number regime."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
