      "rationale": "Formal use-error analysis is not required at MRL 2. Simulation setup was reviewed by a second analyst and documented in the project quality record. No discrepancies were identified."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
