      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty (turbulence model selection, constitutive law for blood viscosity) is acknowledged but not formally quantified at MRL 2. The SST k-ω turbulence model and Carreau-Yasuda viscosity model were selected based on published best-practice guidance for blood-pump CFD."
    },
    {
