      "rationale": "Input parameter uncertainty (hematocrit, viscosity coefficients, pump geometry tolerances) is not formally propagated at MRL 2. Nominal values sourced from ASTM F1841 and manufacturer drawings; a qualitative screening confirmed low sensitivity to ±5% variation in key parameters."
