      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Formal sample-size analysis for the validation experiment is not required at MRL 2. Three independent blood batches were tested at each operating point; batch-to-batch variability in RH was below 6%, consistent with published bovine blood hemolysis literature."
