    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate predictive capability for the relative hemolysis index across the full CPB operating envelope. The screening sensitivity study further supports robustness of the predictions. The model is accepted for use in the regulatory submission to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
